rows.label: qst003102_msg0001
rows.name:
Oh! You'll assist us with our distribution
operations, will you?

rows.label: qst003102_msg0002
rows.name: That's really a great help to us.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0003
rows.name:
The main thing that this place lacks
is cuisine based on fresh vegetables.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0004
rows.name:
If you could find some for us, that
would really improve our service.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0009
rows.name:
We were never this busy before the
Acedian refugees arrived.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0010
rows.name:
Still, I fully understand their
predicament.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0011
rows.name: It's a difficult time for all of us.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0012
rows.name:
These people have no choice.
With Acedia gone, they had to
come here to survive.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0013
rows.name:
In time, they'll make new lives for
themselves here.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0014
rows.name:
We can't just turn them away in their
hour of need.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0015
rows.name:
But, anyway, thanks a lot.
Thanks to you we can do a lot more
to help.

rows.label: qst003102_msg0016
rows.name:
We really need some vegetable-based
meals here. It would be great if you
could provide us with some.
